{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 45528656, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "SOCPL-2023-INFO-REPR", "title": "Information, consultation & participation of representatives of undertakings", "publicationDateLong": 1673308800000, "callIdentifier": "SOCPL-2023-INFO-REPR", "callTitle": "Information, consultation & participation of representatives of undertakings", "callccm2Id": 45528663, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43252517, "abbreviation": "SOCPL", "description": "Social Prerogative and Specific Competencies Lines (SOCPL)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43252542, "abbreviation": "SOCPL-1-1", "description": "SOCPL-1-1"}], "topicMGAs": [], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "SOCPL-PJG SOCPL Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43251093, "abbreviation": "SOCPL-AG", "description": "SOCPL Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "10 January 2023", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["16 March 2023"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3463868": [{"action": "SOCPL-2023-INFO-REPR - SOCPL-PJG SOCPL Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "10 January 2023", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["16 March 2023"], "budgetYearMap": {"2023": 2500000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2023"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">ExpectedOutcome</SPAN>:<p>This call relates to Principle 8 of the European Pillar of Social Rights \u201cSocial dialogue and involvement of workers\u201d, particularly its para (b) \u201cWorkers or their representatives have the right to be informed and consulted in good time on matters relevant to them, in particular on the transfer, restructuring and merger of undertakings and on collective redundancies\u201d. The main priority for the financial year 2023 is to promote actions aimed at developing employees involvement in undertakings in particular by raising awareness and contributing to the application of European Union law and policies in this area and the take-up and development of European Works Councils. This call also aims at supporting projects which seek to identify and address challenges in involving workers resulting from changes in the world of work. </p>\n<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>Promoting actions designed to facilitate the implementation of EU Directives 2002/14, 2001/23, 2009/38, 2001/86, 2003/72, 98/59 and 2001/23 on employee involvement at national and European levels</p>\n", "conditions": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;&#10;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligible countries</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">:&nbsp;as described in the Call document.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;justify;text-indent:-.55pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">EU Member States and in some cases from the European Economic Area (EEA) countries, in accordance with the EEA Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> as described in the Call document.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Applications must be submitted before the <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">call deadline </b>and <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">electronically</b> via the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal Electronic Submission System.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Paper submissions are NOT possible.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Text1\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;tab-stops:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Applications (including annexes and supporting documents) must be submitted using the forms provided <i>inside</i> the Submission System.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Body\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;line-height:14.0pt\"><span class=\"Hyperlink3\"><span lang=\"EN-IE\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE\">Applications must be <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\">complete</b> and contain:<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; margin-left: 40px;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;SimSun;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">Application Form (Part A)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; margin-left: 40px;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;SimSun;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN\">Application Form (Part B)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; margin-left: 40px;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Annexes and supporting documents (to be uploaded as PDF files).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">At proposal submission, the lead applicant will have to confirm that it has the <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\">mandate to act</b> for all applicants; that the information in the application is correct and complete and that the participants comply with the conditions for receiving EU funding (especially eligibility, financial and operational capacity, exclusion, etc). Before signing the grant, each beneficiaries and affiliated entities will have to confirm this again by signing a declaration of honour (DoH). <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">Applications must be <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">readable</b>, <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">accessible and</b> <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\">printable, not exceeding [70] pages</b>. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D;&#10;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluation:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 73, 125); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">as described in the Call document.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D;&#10;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">The <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">award criteria </b>for this call are as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:&#10;-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><span style=\"mso-list:&#10;Ignore\">-<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[e