/span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&ndash; Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your ongoing project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Mar 2, 2023 2:19:47 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Mar 2, 2023 2:19:47 PM", "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">There is an inconsistency between points &ldquo;project budget&rdquo; on page 12 and &ldquo;form of grant&rdquo; on page 16.<br />\r\nThe text on page 12 should be read as follows:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><em>&quot;Project budget:</em>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Project budgets (maximum grant amount) are expected to range between EUR 250<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </s